reviewText: Stunning photography! Lisa's passion and compassion for those she photographs shines through and illuminates your soul!

This is the second in a two part DVD release (the first being "Through The Lens") profiling photographer Lisa Kristine and her travels through 60 countries, sharing her experiences and her intimate photographs of native peoples in their homeland.
I am a big fan of Lisa Kristine's work, and think you will be too.
